Package: InflammationIndex
Type: Package
Title: R Package for Creating an Inflammation Index to Analyse Microglia Morphology
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Devin", "Clarke", email = "devinclarke440@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Devin Clarke <devinclarke440@gmail.com>
Description: Reads in data produced by the Fiji 'Microglia Morphology Analysis' 
  plugin before using it to construct a single metric sensitive to the change present in changing data. 
  This can then be applied to novel data. More information is in the associated publication and README files.
URL: https://github.com/BrainEnergyLab/Inflammation-Index
BugReports: https://github.com/BrainEnergyLab/Inflammation-Index/issues
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    data.table,
    ROCR,
    tidyr
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
